# Tauri bridge

- Call Rust only through `*Service.ts` / feature helpers — never `invoke` from presentational UI.
- Guard with `isTauri()` / `__TAURI_INTERNALS__`; non-Tauri paths no-op or use localStorage.
- Invoke payloads use serde **camelCase** matching TS types.
- Register new commands in `src-tauri/src/lib.rs` `generate_handler!` and capabilities when needed.
- Apply desktop mode via `desktopMode` setting → `sync_native_settings` / `applyNativeSettings`, not ad-hoc window APIs.
- Enabling `desktopMode` also forces `launchOnStartup: true` in `settingsStore`.
- Known tray/events: `navigate-settings`, `desktop-mode-changed`.
- Windows-only embed logic lives behind `#[cfg(windows)]` with stubs elsewhere.
